      "text": [
        " عَلِيٌّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : مَرَّ اَلنَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ عَلَى رَجُلٍ وَ مَعَهُ سِلْعَةٌ يُرِيدُ بَيْعَهَا فَقَالَ \"عَلَيْكَ بِأَوَّلِ اَلسُّوقِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3739 - Imam Ali ibn Abi Talib (as) said:\nThe Prophet (peace be upon him and his family) passed by a man who had goods he wanted to sell and said to him, \"Go to the beginning of the market.\""
        ]
      }
